In order to provide a service,
information is collected and communicated

20
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:40,440
between the components through
a distributed and hierarchical network.

21
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:45,050
Reliability, safety, and
usability of these services

22
00:01:45,050 --> 00:01:48,950
