revealed if not handled carefully.

75
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:10,530
This naturally compromises
the privacy of smart grid users.

76
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:15,130
Similar privacy issues are also present

77
00:06:15,130 --> 00:06:19,660
when transforming data by
aggregating it from multiple owners.

78
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:25,800
From the system performance point of view,
enforcing security and

79
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:29,816
privacy measures leads to
finer granularity of data.

80
00:06:29,816 --> 00:06:35,370
That is more control information
is embedded in data,

81
00:06:35,370 --> 00:06:39,130
and this might cause unacceptable
latencies in some cases.

82
