privacy can change over time.

97
00:07:43,090 --> 00:07:47,020
With this in mind, the system
should be designed in such a way

98
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:50,850
that there is a built in tolerance for
changes in security and

99
00:07:50,850 --> 00:07:55,130
privacy measures for
long-term archive data.

